website_summaries.verdict: Built on a wooden mini ladder structure, it would look great on any kitchen wall.
pros: This unique wall mounted coffee mug holder has a beautifully rustic feel on a wooden mini ladder structure that would look great on any kitchen wall
cons: Some found that the hooks were placed too close together, not allowing for adequate space between cups
